Generate a Bill for Vohra's Purchase
Vohra went to a movie with his friends and bought pizzas, puffs, and cool drinks during the break. Given the prices
Rs. 100 per pizza
Rs. 20 per puff
Rs. 10 per cooldrink
Generate a bill for what Vohra has bought.
#Sample Input 1
Enter the number of pizzas bought: 10
Enter the number of puffs bought: 12
Enter the number of cool drinks bought: 5
Sample Output 1
Number of pizzas: 10
Number of puffs: 12
Number of cooldrinks: 5
Total price: 1290

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
public class cs{
	
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner sc= new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.println("Enter the Number of Pizza's bought :");
		int pizzaBought = sc.nextInt();
		System.out.println("Enter the Number of puff's bought :");
		int puffBought =sc.nextInt();
		System.out.println("Enter the number of cooldrink's bought :");
		int cooldrinkBought =sc.nextInt();
		
		int bill = (pizzaBought*100) + (puffBought*20) + (cooldrinkBought*10);
		System.out.println("Nubmer of pizzas :"+ pizzaBought);
		System.out.println("Nubmer of Puffs :"+ puffBought);
		System.out.println("Nubmer of cooldrinks :"+ cooldrinkBought);
		System.out.println("Total Price :"+ bill);
	}
}

